batrun (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add `batrun report` with --last/--since/--month/--year/--all windows.
    Aggregates awake-on-battery drain into projected 100%-charge runtime,
    reports suspend drain and battery health separately.
  * Add `batrun status` showing current battery, instantaneous draw, and
    projected remaining time using both `power_now` and a historical
    30-day average.

 -- Jerko Čilaš <jerko@cilas.me>  Tue, 19 May 2026 17:30:00 +0000

